â€” Chosen (@MikeChosen1) February 22, 2017 Advertisement - Continue Reading Below At a recent date auction for the Nigerian Student Association (NSA) at the University of Houston, Twitter user @MikeChosen1, whose real name is Michael Akinyemi, filmed a truly incredible moment. In doing so, he introduced the world to #BootBae, who quite frankly would raise her boot and say, "No, thank you, not today," to all other viral videos. She is it! She is perfect!
In the video, one of the women auctioning herself off for a date walks up to a guy sat in the front row, about to strut her stuff and make her case for a bid. But nope, his girlfriend straight-up lifted her leg into the air to block her path. The fact that she is wearing the world's fiercest red suede thigh-high boots only adds to the glorious savagery of this exchange.
She.
